 * RECONCILE IN PUTTY (ground truth):                                        *
 *   find /sas/broc /sas/RSD -type f -name "*.sas7bdat" 2>/dev/null | wc -l  *
 *   find /sas/broc -type f \( -name "*.log" -o -name "*.lst" \) 2>/dev/null \*
 *       | wc -l                                                             *
 *                                                                           *
